data.description: One level living with hardwood floors throughout in great East Paulding location close to shopping, dining, and schools.  The yard is peaceful and park-like. Covered front porch is a great place to relax.  The family friendly living room has inviting stone fireplace and is open to the dining room.  Dining room is spacious and a wonderful place to host family or friends.   The kitchen has painted cabinets, lots of counter space, and there is a desk area.   There is a separate breakfast area.  The spacious owner's bedroom has extra built-in storage cabinet.   Secondary bedrooms are nicely sized.
